When light comes into the eye,

00:24:43.610 --> 00:24:46.630
there's a particular group
of retinal ganglion cells,

00:24:46.630 --> 00:24:48.950
or type of retinal ganglion cells,

00:24:48.950 --> 00:24:51.790
