there's going to be so
much photon light energy

00:30:55.230 --> 00:30:56.700
arriving on your retina

00:30:56.700 --> 00:30:58.860
that it probably only
takes 30 to 60 seconds

00:30:58.860 --> 00:31:00.480
to trigger the central clock

00:31:00.480 --> 00:31:03.120
and set your cortisol and
melatonin rhythms properly

00:31:03.120 --> 00:31:06.163
and get everything lined up nicely,

00:31:07.210 --> 00:31:10.000
