it is eventually converted
into a certain form of energy

00:44:42.330 --> 00:44:43.990
that all your cells use,

00:44:43.990 --> 00:44:45.760
but you don't take glucose,

00:44:45.760 --> 00:44:49.070
you don't take bread or
a steak or a nice orange

00:44:49.070 --> 00:44:50.350
and shove it in your ear,

00:44:50.350 --> 00:44:51.300
you put it in your mouth,

00:44:51.300 --> 00:44:53.150
it goes into your stomach, it's digested,

00:44:53.150 --> 00:44:55.700
and then that resource is distributed

00:44:55.700 --> 00:44:57.530
to all the cells of your body.

00:44:57.530 --> 00:44:59.910
Every cell in your body needs oxygen,

