because there's some
good information there

00:53:50.830 --> 00:53:52.740
about how they can protect themselves

00:53:52.740 --> 00:53:56.340
against some of the very bad
health effects of shift work,

00:53:56.340 --> 00:53:57.830
of getting light in the
middle of the night,

00:53:57.830 --> 00:53:59.210
but we rely on shift workers

00:53:59.210 --> 00:54:01.440
and they're super important to culture

00:54:01.440 --> 00:54:03.470
and society and the economy,

00:54:03.470 --> 00:54:05.050
so I wanna acknowledge them

